critical_fixes.description:
The zone map skip condition is backwards. Current code skips blocks where max_date < date_cutoff, but the filter is 'o_orderdate < date_cutoff', meaning we WANT orders before the cutoff. These are exactly the blocks being skipped! Correct logic: skip blocks where min_date >= date_cutoff (all dates in block fail the < cutoff filter). Change line 187 from:
  if (m < zone_map.size() && zone_map[m].second < date_cutoff)
to:
  if (m < zone_map.size() && zone_map[m].first >= date_cutoff)
